### Login as Warehouse staff
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "warehouse@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Save token
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1. Get pending export orders (Chờ xuất kho - CONFIRMED)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/orders/pending-export?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get exported orders (Đã xuất kho - SHIPPING)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/orders/exported?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get order detail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/orders/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
